OOC: I might've missed that post rAuq.

IC: Skullgrin hears a familiar voice, but only a small bit familiar.  He
looks at Condor.  He was asleep(I think).  Oh well, the cage would keep him
from escaping anytime soon.  So Skullgrin ran outside.  He saw Switchblade,
and ran up to him.

       "What do you want?  You ally or foe?" He questioned.

       This bot looked oddly familiar, but SKullgrin just couldn't put his
finger on who it was.
